FACING THE LAST TRUMP!
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    Having noted President Trump's rather gung-ho, fire and fury
    attitude to nuclear deterrent and the possibility that he might
    wake up at 3.00am one morning, reach for the Twitter button on his
    mobile phone (I was going to say 'smart phone' but clearly 'Smart'
    and 'Trump' do not sit very well together) and inadvertently
    trigger World War 3. I decided to dig out my battered copy of Civil
    Defence Handbook No. 10 "Advising the Householder on Protection
    against Nuclear Attack" and swot up... just in case.

