CHANGES AT TWICKENHAM STATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    From 25 August, the station entrance has moved. Access to trains,
    ticket machines and other services will be via a temporary
    construction next to platform three (near the car park).

    In addition, near the temporary station entrance there will be one
    Blue Badge holders bay, one 'Kiss &amp; Ride' bay as well as two
    spaces for taxi set down and pick-ups. Replacement cycle parking
    facilities are also being provided.

